title: you’re gonna hate me
lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet
[Verse 1]
Called it quits a week ago
Don't pretend you found my love, already know
You got a vendetta against me, killing you gently
Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah
('Cause) I knew a guy when I left you
He came around sometimes, you knew him too
You were always suspicious, never cool with it
Ah-ah, ah-ah, ah-ah
[Pre-Chorus]
And I don't wanna, I don't wanna, I don't wanna tell you the truth
Know it's gonna, know it's gonna, I know what it's gonna do
[Chorus]
You're gonna hate me
Don't blame you, baby
Just how God made me
I move on too soon
Tell your friends I'm crazy
And that I'm never happy
And yeah, if I could date me
I'd probably hate me too

[Verse 2]
Therе's one more thing I wanna say
I promise that I rеally love—
